name: Euronyl® 74 EN
description: Euronyl® 74 EN Silicone-free is applied in the field of paints & varnish, toys. It's special features are that it has low VOC and free of APEO, raw materials are conform to EN 71.3 and EN 71.9. It has very wide compatibility in numerous systems.

Synonyms: 2-[2-(2-Methoxy-4-nitrophenyl)diazenyl]-N-(2-methoxyphenyl)-3-oxobutanamide, C.I. Pigment Yellow 74, Sunbrite Yellow 74, C.I. 11741, C.I. PY 74, PY 74
